</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="DC367959B3A869B0F7E468CC3DCD38ED" bold="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">A</emphasis>
young plant with the cotyledons and two palmate leaves 
<emphasis id="4F6C9D649DCA841F8EAA694E63B92125" bold="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">B</emphasis>
young inflorescence with floral buds subtended by a bract and bracteoles 
<emphasis id="0B5EE87E43C8A7BEB477180F030CD746" bold="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">C</emphasis>
