<emphasis id="7F282B5ADB490F948C1C719F6DF69F9E" bold="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">E</emphasis>
three follicles 
<emphasis id="1A325034541EF6C419F9FF55E8CAA77D" bold="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">F</emphasis>
